{"tid":1286850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【引渡惡法】涉圍警總被控三罪「畫家」帶淚抵法庭","createTime":"2019-07-05T03:44:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T05:27:59.000Z","uid":143526,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0a5d27bf6547d6c12388069855016176242d67c8","tid":1286850,"uid":143526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:44:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190705/large/1562296984_03a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190705%2Flarge%2F1562296984_03a3.jpg&h=77a17eaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方就上月本港連串的示威行動進行大搜捕，其中有「畫家」之稱的男子因涉包圍警總事件被拘控，今早由警車押送到東區裁判法院提堂。被告被控襲警、刑事毀壞及在公眾地方作出擾亂秩序的行為三罪，其中控罪指他向警務人員舉中指及呼籲他人給他雞蛋以擲向警員。<br />\n<br />\n全文: <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190705&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59790270\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190705%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59790270&d=J%2B7a%2FypYnyyex2M81OHxVWWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=9d748b6f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190705%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59790270&h=40af5290\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190705&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59790270</a>"},{"pid":"31fa39f2d376164bc97dc0e55da674f6bdcf5176","tid":1286850,"uid":997,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:45:12.000Z","msg":"舉中指有咩問題?"},{"pid":"ae78a3e5bdc38653d1a6432b00718a1caa4ce103","tid":1286850,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f5ddba935290010206f8e62bbf58030a8c051d","tid":1286850,"uid":45910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:55:34.000Z","msg":"舉中指係襲警定擾亂秩序<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6406046401323f1a9415ee2f08aa4c496eef6a","tid":1286850,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:57:41.000Z","msg":"(綜合報道)(星島日報報道)佔旺「畫家」潘運瑭，涉嫌非禮一名中度智障女子，今早於九龍城裁判法院承認兩項非禮罪，被判入獄10個月。<br />\n<br />\n案件中的受害人X是一名年約40歲的中度智障女子，與潘屬情侶關係，兩人於佔領旺角時結識。潘於去年10月31日，在旺角強吻及胸襲X。由於潘有案底，亦曾被監禁，故被裁判官判入獄10個月。<br />\n<br />\n？？？"},{"pid":"f8f11b02fb76e0fe5bcb984bd8bc1262e00c4b00","tid":1286850,"uid":213142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:00:24.000Z","msg":"涉嫌舉中指？"},{"pid":"dd39e51e52e0fa5f4b049007176b4e14a64cc649","tid":1286850,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:04:42.000Z","msg":"「七黑」團結打倒白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1284973\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1284973</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zm1ytZc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzm1ytZc.jpg&h=68603869&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"982635d57d98abb2bdacf7c60a95b88d6f8b506f","tid":1286850,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:07:03.000Z","msg":"舉中指可以告乜？歧視？"},{"pid":"80ec5249307f14b7bb1159c63da1210be6f9a73a","tid":1286850,"uid":152584,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:10:49.000Z","msg":"雖然佢有小小問題 但我地係同路人 要支持佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7fbc6b3080faf0f38ca078f82c4a26361465d54","tid":1286850,"uid":149361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:20:49.000Z","msg":"狗方又鳩落charge"},{"pid":"fa115a195121d2c0484c34081585671d8e10203c","tid":1286850,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:17:22.000Z","msg":"舉中指可以點告得入?<br />\n依條罪如果入左好撚大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"433550efac88a16a4a26134a6e8b06bec44976b1","tid":1286850,"uid":70336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:22:14.000Z","msg":"亞一其實係咪諗住鳩告人